   above example, the JSON object takes the following format before itâ€™s JWT encoded:</p>
  <codeblock>{
"url": "https://dev.livefyre.com/articles/test.html", 
"articleId": "1", 
"type": "livechat", 
"title": "Title 1"
}</codeblock>
 </conbody>
